{"pageId":"47a67125e39e3b94","url":"https://www.cms.gov/Regulations-a%3Cp%3E08/2016%20-%20This%20change%20request%20(CR)%20is%20the%209th%20maintenance%20update%20of%20ICD-10%20conversions%20and%20other%20coding%20updates%20specific%20to%20national%20coverage%20determinations%20(NCDs).%20The%20majority%20of%20the%20NCDs%20included%20are%20a%20result%20of%20feedback%20received%20from%20previous%20ICD-10%20NCD%20CR7818,%20CR8109,%20CR8197,%20CR8691,%20CR9087,%20CR9252,%20CR9540,%20and%20CR9631.%20Some%20are%20the%20result%20of%20revisions%20required%20to%20other%20NCD-related%20CRs%20released%20separately.%3Cbr%3E%20%20%20Edits%20to%20ICD-10%20and%20other%20coding%20updates%20specific%20to%20NCDs%20will%20be%20included%20in%20subsequent,%20quarterly%20releases%20as%20needed.%20No%20policy-related%20changes%20are%20included%20with%20these%20updates.%20Any%20policy-related%20changes%20to%20NCDs%20continue%20to%20be%20implemented%20via%20the%20current,%20long-standing%20NCD%20process.%20%20(%3Ca%20href=","week":"2026-W25","runId":"2026-06-18T18-27-14-023Z-b6fe8a","scannedAt":"2026-06-18T18:27:26.539Z","status":404,"depth":6}